## 12. API Documentation

### 12.1 Base URL
All API endpoints are prefixed with: `http://localhost:8080/api`

### 12.2 Authentication Endpoints

**POST /api/auth/register**
- Description: Register a new user account
- Authentication: Not required
- Request Body:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890"
}
```
- Response: 201 Created
```json
{
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "role": "CUSTOMER",
  "message": "Registration successful"
}
```

**POST /api/auth/login**
- Description: Authenticate user and receive JWT token
- Authentication: Not required
- Request Body:
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```
- Response: 200 OK
```json
{
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "role": "CUSTOMER",
  "message": "Login successful"
}
```

### 12.3 Product Endpoints

**GET /api/products**
- Description: Retrieve all active products
- Authentication: Not required
- Response: 200 OK
```json
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Laptop",
    "description": "High-performance laptop",
    "price": 999.99,
    "stockQuantity": 50,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "brand": "TechBrand",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
    "active": true,
    "createdAt": "2024-01-01T10:00:00",
    "updatedAt": "2024-01-01T10:00:00"
  }
]
```

**GET /api/products/{id}**
- Description: Retrieve product by ID
- Authentication: Not required
- Response: 200 OK (ProductResponse) or 404 Not Found

**GET /api/products/search?keyword={keyword}**
- Description: Search products by keyword
- Authentication: Not required
- Response: 200 OK (List of ProductResponse)

**GET /api/products/category/{category}**
- Description: Get products by category
- Authentication: Not required
- Response: 200 OK (List of ProductResponse)

**POST /api/products**
- Description: Create new product (Admin only)
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Request Body: ProductRequest
- Response: 201 Created (ProductResponse) or 403 Forbidden

**PUT /api/products/{id}**
- Description: Update product (Admin only)
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Request Body: ProductRequest
- Response: 200 OK (ProductResponse) or 403 Forbidden

**DELETE /api/products/{id}**
- Description: Delete product (Admin only)
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Response: 204 No Content or 403 Forbidden

### 12.4 Cart Endpoints

**POST /api/cart/add**
- Description: Add item to shopping cart
- Authentication: Required
- Request Body:
```json
{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}
```
- Response: 200 OK
```json
{
  "message": "Item added to cart successfully",
  "cartItems": 1
}
```

**GET /api/cart**
- Description: Get user's shopping cart
- Authentication: Required
- Response: 200 OK
```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "product": {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Laptop",
        "price": 999.99
      },
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 1999.98,
  "itemCount": 1
}
```

**DELETE /api/cart/item/{cartItemId}**
- Description: Remove item from cart
- Authentication: Required
- Response: 200 OK

**DELETE /api/cart/clear**
- Description: Clear entire cart
- Authentication: Required
- Response: 200 OK

### 12.5 Order Endpoints

**POST /api/orders**
- Description: Create order from cart
- Authentication: Required
- Request Body:
```json
{
  "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, City, Country",
  "paymentMethod": "Credit Card"
}
```
- Response: 201 Created
```json
{
  "orderId": 1,
  "totalAmount": 1999.98,
  "status": "PENDING",
  "message": "Order created successfully"
}
```

**GET /api/orders**
- Description: Get user's order history
- Authentication: Required
- Response: 200 OK (List of orders)

**GET /api/orders/{orderId}**
- Description: Get order by ID
- Authentication: Required
- Response: 200 OK (Order details) or 404 Not Found

**PUT /api/orders/{orderId}/status?status={status}**
- Description: Update order status (Admin only)
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Query Parameters: status (PENDING, CONFIRMED, SHIPPED, DELIVERED, CANCELLED)
- Response: 200 OK or 403 Forbidden

### 12.6 Admin Endpoints

**GET /api/admin/orders**
- Description: Get all orders in system
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Response: 200 OK (List of all orders) or 403 Forbidden

**GET /api/admin/orders/status/{status}**
- Description: Get orders filtered by status
- Authentication: Required (Admin role)
- Response: 200 OK (List of orders) or 403 Forbidden

### 12.7 Error Responses

**400 Bad Request:**
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Validation failed",
  "errors": {
    "email": "Email is required",
    "password": "Password must be at least 6 characters"
  }
}
```

**401 Unauthorized:**
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Unauthorized access"
}
```

**403 Forbidden:**
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Access denied. Admin role required."
}
```

**404 Not Found:**
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "Product not found with id: 1"
}
```

**500 Internal Server Error:**
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "An unexpected error occurred",
  "details": "Error details"
}
```

